# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_NOT_STEALABLE_AMBIENTLY

## Summary
Sets a vehicle so that it can't be stealable by an ambient ped

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** stealable
